{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"59ea3ccf-f75b-4b91-b77f-be5909d5a21a","content":"No files found in the workspace. Since there's no existing file, here's how to convert your page to compiled bindings:\n\n## Add `x:DataType` to your XAML\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout Padding=\"20\" Spacing=\"15\">\n        <Entry Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Slider Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"48\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\nThe key change is adding `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the `ContentPage` element. This tells the XAML compiler the expected type for all `{Binding}` expressions in scope.\n\n## Catching binding errors at build time\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <!-- Emit warnings for bindings that can't be compiled -->\n  <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nThen **treat those warnings as errors** so they break the build:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <WarningsAsErrors>XC0045;XC0022</WarningsAsErrors>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n| What happens | Without `x:DataType` | With `x:DataType` |\n|---|---|---|\n| Typo like `{Binding Thme}` | Silent runtime failure | **Build error** |\n| Wrong type (e.g., binding `int` to `IsToggled`) | Runtime mismatch | **Build warning/error** |\n\nWith compiled bindings the compiler resolves property paths at build time — any misspelled or missing property on `SettingsViewModel` will fail compilation rather than silently producing a blank control at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7bc5cfce-17f1-4442-ab8b-244a16e06105","outputTokens":536,"requestId":"E857:DF52E:271873F:2B192B6:69F93E2D"},"id":"9bdf90f2-fa7e-4b5f-acfd-01bfbfc96402","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:47:52.857Z","parentId":"417ba5a0-2ba9-43e1-909c-51239881a896"}
